{"type": "article", "id": 19332, "title": "方圆桌椅", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-18T07:30:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 41, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122353QEACJBWUYMsI2v5q.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是中国设计师李培新带来的方圆桌椅，有胡桃木和榉木两种材料。桌面和座位面都是将圆形和方形结合，有一个圆润的轮廓，从侧面看过去非常轻盈，给人柔和的居家感受。此外，在桌腿和桌面的连接处采用榫卯技术，有柔和的弧度。桌椅都搭配了多种颜色，售价 899 元起，<a href=\"http://item.taobao.com/item.htm?spm=a1z10.1-c.w10688964-12393918591.6.pSQHGk&amp;id=523216359520\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145845Ln0WBUj8pgGaIxF5.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1105\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.02314815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145847Ta5diyF9H4PmSkXJ.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1620\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261458479bU7sIezBCxuMSnQ.jpg\" width=\"580\" height=\"355\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.61206897\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145848W6XZs0MoItVCydKH.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"720\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}